3311 appropriated in fiscal year 2026-27 to the Department of Health and Human Services to
3322 replace current and anticipated reduction in grants to the department under the federal
3333 victim assistance formula grant program that are not needed for those purposes must be
3344 equally disbursed to a statewide coalition of domestic violence resource centers and a
